name: Adorable Diapers Personalized Baby Diapers Gift Basket
description:
You design! We create! 

We personalize disposable baby diapers and present them in huge half bushel gift baskets! Each contains 30 diapers; sized 1, 2, and 3 for the ever-growing baby and those awesome photo ops!

You tell us the baby's name and we will take it from there! Or visit us at www.AdorableDiapers.com for options and colors...

Trust us, we've been doing this a lonnnnnnng time! If your baby is a rock star, we will totally rock it out -- with good taste of course! And if yours is a dancer or more traditional in taste, we know exactly what you'll love!
